import { Button, Box, TextField } from "@mui/material";

export default function TaskForm(): JSX.Element {
    return (
        <Box sx={{position: "fixed", top: 1/4, left: 1/4, width: 1/2, height: 1/2}}>
            <>
                <TextField>
                    Name
                </TextField>
            </>
            <TextField>
                Description
            </TextField>
            <TextField>
                Due time
            </TextField>
            <Button>
                Submit
            </Button>
        </Box>
    );
}
